<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='975000' id='t-975000'>That's why they don't know whether their mutual fund manager</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='977000' id='t-977000'>is taking 0.1 percent or 0.15 percent of their investment,</span>
