17:59
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1068000' id='t-1068000'>The problem of shifting comparisons is even more difficult</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1071000' id='t-1071000'>when these choices are arrayed over time.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1074000' id='t-1074000'>People have a lot of trouble making decisions</span>
