<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1090000' id='t-1090000'>Here's the first easy problem:</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1093000' id='t-1093000'>You can have 60 dollars now or 50 dollars now. Which would you prefer?</span>
