<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1202000' id='t-1202000'>These guys can tell us.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1203000' id='t-1203000'>What you see here are two lads,</span>
