<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1259000' id='t-1259000'>As Plato said, what space is to size, time is to value.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1264000' id='t-1264000'>These are the results of the hard problem I gave you:</span>
