<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1271000' id='t-1271000'>And these are subjective values,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1272000' id='t-1272000'>and what you can see is, our two rules are preserved.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
