<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1274000' id='t-1274000'>People always think more is better than less:</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1276000' id='t-1276000'>60 is always better than 50,</span>
