</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
22:19
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1328000' id='t-1328000'>The answer to this question, I think, is an answer you've already heard</span>
